headline: Paysafe and Fiserv Strengthen Partnership to Drive SMB Growth with Enhanced Capital Access, Fraud Protection, and New Digital Wallet Solution
summary: LONDON, May 09, 2025--Paysafe (NYSE: PSFE), a leading payments platform, and Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE: FI), a global provider of payments and financial services technology solutions, are expanding their long-term partnership to deliver even greater value to their customers. This collaboration includes several key initiatives focused on empowering small and medium-sized businesses (SMBs).
